- Need nodejs and npm
- install testcafe globally in local to run testcafe
npm install -g testcafe
- create package.json (-y will install with default setting and will not ask user for input)
npm init -y
- install testcafe dev dependency
npm install testcafe --save-dev
- run testcase
testcafe source-test-file.js
- to enable live mode to reload test as you edit them, it will keep brouser window open and restart test as you save the file
testcafe source-test-file.js --live
- CTRL + S
stops the current test case
- CTRL + R
restarts current test run
- CTRL + W
turns the file watcher on and off
- CTRl + C
close live mode
